wish i had switched from the switch ! ! ! have read several leonard books and this may be the worst one i have read . the two so called `` bad men '' remind me of my self if i tried to do what they did . nothing goes right . ordell robbie and louis gara grab mickey dawson , wife of frank dawson , to hold for ransom . frank could care less . he has a mistress and does not want his wife back . this makes mickey very upset and she decides she wants part of the action with ordell and louis . meanwhile , the mistress decides she wants to be part of their plan too . you will meet crazy richard , who likes to shoot people . there was page after page of just talk . nothing happening . i kept thinking it would get better but no such luck . if you are having trouble sleeping try this book